headline: Eaton Cummins Automated Transmission Technologies Celebrates 500,000th Endurant Transmission Milestone with Werner
summary: GALESBURG, Mich., August 20, 2025--Eaton Cummins has produced its 500,000th Endurant transmission for the on-highway and vocational markets. Endurant transmissions debuted in 2017.
